{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"For a long time,"},{"time":2000,"text":"there was me, and my body."},{"time":6000,"text":"Me was composed of stories,"},{"time":9000,"text":"of cravings, of strivings,"},{"time":11000,"text":"of desires of the future."},{"time":13000,"text":"Me was trying"},{"time":15000,"text":"not to be an outcome of my violent past,"},{"time":18000,"text":"but the separation that had already occurred"},{"time":20000,"text":"between me and my body"},{"time":22000,"text":"was a pretty significant outcome."},{"time":25000,"text":"Me was always trying to become something, somebody."},{"time":28000,"text":"Me only existed in the trying."},{"time":31000,"text":"My body was often in the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34000,"text":"Me was a floating head."},{"time":36000,"text":"For years, I actually only wore hats."},{"time":39000,"text":"It was a way of keeping my head attached."},{"time":41000,"text":"It was a way of locating myself."},{"time":44000,"text":"I worried that [if] I took my hat off"},{"time":46000,"text":"I wouldn't be here anymore."},{"time":48000,"text":"I actually had a therapist who once said to me,"},{"time":51000,"text":"\"Eve, you've been coming here for two years,"},{"time":53000,"text":"and, to be honest, it never occurred to me that you had a body.\""},{"time":56000,"text":"All this time I lived in the city"},{"time":58000,"text":"because, to be honest,"},{"time":60000,"text":"I was afraid of trees."},{"time":62000,"text":"I never had babies"},{"time":64000,"text":"because heads cannot give birth."},{"time":66000,"text":"Babies actually don't come out of your mouth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69000,"text":"As I had no reference point for my body,"},{"time":72000,"text":"I began to ask other women about their bodies --"},{"time":75000,"text":"in particular, their vaginas,"},{"time":77000,"text":"because I thought vaginas were kind of important."},{"time":79000,"text":"This led to me writing \"The Vagina Monologues,\""},{"time":81000,"text":"which led to me obsessively and incessantly"},{"time":84000,"text":"talking about vaginas everywhere I could."},{"time":87000,"text":"I did this in front of many strangers."},{"time":90000,"text":"One night on stage,"},{"time":92000,"text":"I actually entered my vagina."},{"time":95000,"text":"It was an ecstatic experience."},{"time":98000,"text":"It scared me, it energized me,"},{"time":101000,"text":"and then I became a driven person,"},{"time":104000,"text":"a driven vagina."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"I began to see my body like a thing,"},{"time":109000,"text":"a thing that could move fast,"},{"time":111000,"text":"like a thing that could accomplish other things,"},{"time":113000,"text":"many things, all at once."},{"time":116000,"text":"I began to see my body like an iPad or a car."},{"time":119000,"text":"I would drive it and demand things from it."},{"time":121000,"text":"It had no limits. It was invincible."},{"time":124000,"text":"It was to be conquered and mastered like the Earth herself."},{"time":127000,"text":"I didn't heed it;"},{"time":129000,"text":"no, I organized it and I directed it."},{"time":131000,"text":"I didn't have patience for my body;"},{"time":133000,"text":"I snapped it into shape."},{"time":135000,"text":"I was greedy."},{"time":137000,"text":"I took more than my body had to offer."},{"time":139000,"text":"If I was tired, I drank more espressos."},{"time":142000,"text":"If I was afraid, I went to more dangerous places."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"Oh sure, sure, I had moments of appreciation of my body,"},{"time":148000,"text":"the way an abusive parent"},{"time":150000,"text":"can sometimes have a moment of kindness."},{"time":152000,"text":"My father was really kind to me"},{"time":154000,"text":"on my 16th birthday, for example."},{"time":156000,"text":"I heard people murmur from time to time"},{"time":158000,"text":"that I should love my body,"},{"time":160000,"text":"so I learned how to do this."},{"time":162000,"text":"I was a vegetarian, I was sober, I didn't smoke."},{"time":165000,"text":"But all that was just a more sophisticated way"},{"time":167000,"text":"to manipulate my body --"},{"time":169000,"text":"a further disassociation,"},{"time":171000,"text":"like planting a vegetable field on a freeway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"As a result of me talking so much about my vagina,"},{"time":179000,"text":"many women started to tell me about theirs --"},{"time":182000,"text":"their stories about their bodies."},{"time":184000,"text":"Actually, these stories compelled me around the world,"},{"time":187000,"text":"and I've been to over 60 countries."},{"time":189000,"text":"I heard thousands of stories,"},{"time":191000,"text":"and I have to tell you, there was always this moment"},{"time":193000,"text":"where the women shared with me"},{"time":195000,"text":"that particular moment when she separated from her body --"},{"time":199000,"text":"when she left home."},{"time":201000,"text":"I heard about women being molested in their beds,"},{"time":205000,"text":"flogged in their burqas,"},{"time":207000,"text":"left for dead in parking lots,"},{"time":209000,"text":"acid burned in their kitchens."},{"time":211000,"text":"Some women became quiet and disappeared."},{"time":214000,"text":"Other women became mad, driven machines like me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"In the middle of my traveling,"},{"time":220000,"text":"I turned 40 and I began to hate my body,"},{"time":222000,"text":"which was actually progress,"},{"time":224000,"text":"because at least my body existed enough to hate it."},{"time":227000,"text":"Well my stomach -- it was my stomach I hated."},{"time":230000,"text":"It was proof that I had not measured up,"},{"time":233000,"text":"that I was old and not fabulous and not perfect"},{"time":236000,"text":"or able to fit into the predetermined corporate image in shape."},{"time":240000,"text":"My stomach was proof that I had failed,"},{"time":243000,"text":"that it had failed me, that it was broken."},{"time":246000,"text":"My life became about getting rid of it and obsessing about getting rid of it."},{"time":249000,"text":"In fact, it became so extreme"},{"time":251000,"text":"I wrote a play about it."},{"time":253000,"text":"But the more I talked about it,"},{"time":255000,"text":"the more objectified and fragmented my body became."},{"time":258000,"text":"It became entertainment; it became a new kind of commodity,"},{"time":261000,"text":"something I was selling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264000,"text":"Then I went somewhere else."},{"time":266000,"text":"I went outside"},{"time":268000,"text":"what I thought I knew."},{"time":270000,"text":"I went to the Democratic Republic of Congo."},{"time":274000,"text":"And I heard stories"},{"time":276000,"text":"that shattered all the other stories."},{"time":278000,"text":"I heard stories"},{"time":280000,"text":"that got inside my body."},{"time":282000,"text":"I heard about a little girl"},{"time":284000,"text":"who couldn't stop peeing on herself"},{"time":286000,"text":"because so many grown soldiers"},{"time":288000,"text":"had shoved themselves inside her."},{"time":291000,"text":"I heard an 80-year-old woman"},{"time":293000,"text":"whose legs were broken and pulled out of her sockets"},{"time":296000,"text":"and twisted up on her head"},{"time":298000,"text":"as the soldiers raped her like that."},{"time":300000,"text":"There are thousands of these stories,"},{"time":302000,"text":"and many of the women had holes in their bodies --"},{"time":305000,"text":"holes, fistula --"},{"time":307000,"text":"that were the violation of war --"},{"time":310000,"text":"holes in the fabric of their souls."},{"time":313000,"text":"These stories saturated my cells and nerves,"},{"time":316000,"text":"and to be honest,"},{"time":318000,"text":"I stopped sleeping for three years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"All the stories began to bleed together."},{"time":323000,"text":"The raping of the Earth,"},{"time":325000,"text":"the pillaging of minerals,"},{"time":327000,"text":"the destruction of vaginas --"},{"time":329000,"text":"none of these were separate anymore"},{"time":332000,"text":"from each other or me."},{"time":334000,"text":"Militias were raping six-month-old babies"},{"time":337000,"text":"so that countries far away"},{"time":339000,"text":"could get access to gold and coltan"},{"time":341000,"text":"for their iPhones and computers."},{"time":344000,"text":"My body had not only become a driven machine,"},{"time":347000,"text":"but it was responsible now"},{"time":349000,"text":"for destroying other women's bodies"},{"time":351000,"text":"in its mad quest to make more machines"},{"time":353000,"text":"to support the speed and efficiency of my machine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357000,"text":"Then I got cancer --"},{"time":359000,"text":"or I found out I had cancer."},{"time":361000,"text":"It arrived like a speeding bird"},{"time":363000,"text":"smashing into a windowpane."},{"time":366000,"text":"Suddenly, I had a body,"},{"time":368000,"text":"a body that was pricked"},{"time":370000,"text":"and poked and punctured,"},{"time":372000,"text":"a body that was cut wide open,"},{"time":375000,"text":"a body that had organs removed"},{"time":377000,"text":"and transported and rearranged and reconstructed,"},{"time":380000,"text":"a body that was scanned"},{"time":382000,"text":"and had tubes shoved down it,"},{"time":384000,"text":"a body that was burning from chemicals."},{"time":387000,"text":"Cancer exploded"},{"time":389000,"text":"the wall of my disconnection."},{"time":392000,"text":"I suddenly understood that the crisis in my body"},{"time":395000,"text":"was the crisis in the world,"},{"time":397000,"text":"and it wasn't happening later,"},{"time":399000,"text":"it was happening now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401000,"text":"Suddenly, my cancer was a cancer that was everywhere,"},{"time":404000,"text":"the cancer of cruelty, the cancer of greed,"},{"time":407000,"text":"the cancer that gets inside people"},{"time":409000,"text":"who live down the streets from chemical plants -- and they're usually poor --"},{"time":413000,"text":"the cancer inside the coal miner's lungs,"},{"time":415000,"text":"the cancer of stress for not achieving enough,"},{"time":418000,"text":"the cancer of buried trauma,"},{"time":420000,"text":"the cancer in caged chickens and polluted fish,"},{"time":423000,"text":"the cancer in women's uteruses from being raped,"},{"time":426000,"text":"the cancer that is everywhere from our carelessness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429000,"text":"In his new and visionary book,"},{"time":432000,"text":"\"New Self, New World,\""},{"time":434000,"text":"the writer Philip Shepherd says,"},{"time":436000,"text":"\"If you are divided from your body,"},{"time":439000,"text":"you are also divided from the body of the world,"},{"time":442000,"text":"which then appears to be other than you"},{"time":444000,"text":"or separate from you,"},{"time":446000,"text":"rather than the living continuum"},{"time":448000,"text":"to which you belong.\""},{"time":450000,"text":"Before cancer,"},{"time":452000,"text":"the world was something other."},{"time":454000,"text":"It was as if I was living in a stagnant pool"},{"time":457000,"text":"and cancer dynamited the boulder"},{"time":459000,"text":"that was separating me from the larger sea."},{"time":462000,"text":"Now I am swimming in it."},{"time":465000,"text":"Now I lay down in the grass"},{"time":467000,"text":"and I rub my body in it,"},{"time":469000,"text":"and I love the mud on my legs and feet."},{"time":472000,"text":"Now I make a daily pilgrimage"},{"time":475000,"text":"to visit a particular weeping willow by the Seine,"},{"time":478000,"text":"and I hunger for the green fields"},{"time":480000,"text":"in the bush outside Bukavu."},{"time":482000,"text":"And when it rains hard rain,"},{"time":484000,"text":"I scream and I run in circles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"I know that everything is connected,"},{"time":491000,"text":"and the scar that runs the length of my torso"},{"time":494000,"text":"is the markings of the earthquake."},{"time":496000,"text":"And I am there with the three million in the streets of Port-au-Prince."},{"time":500000,"text":"And the fire that burned in me"},{"time":502000,"text":"on day three through six of chemo"},{"time":505000,"text":"is the fire that is burning"},{"time":507000,"text":"in the forests of the world."},{"time":509000,"text":"I know that the abscess"},{"time":511000,"text":"that grew around my wound after the operation,"},{"time":514000,"text":"the 16 ounces of puss,"},{"time":516000,"text":"is the contaminated Gulf of Mexico,"},{"time":519000,"text":"and there were oil-drenched pelicans inside me"},{"time":522000,"text":"and dead floating fish."},{"time":524000,"text":"And the catheters they shoved into me without proper medication"},{"time":527000,"text":"made me scream out"},{"time":529000,"text":"the way the Earth cries out from the drilling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533000,"text":"In my second chemo,"},{"time":535000,"text":"my mother got very sick"},{"time":537000,"text":"and I went to see her."},{"time":539000,"text":"And in the name of connectedness,"},{"time":541000,"text":"the only thing she wanted before she died"},{"time":544000,"text":"was to be brought home"},{"time":546000,"text":"by her beloved Gulf of Mexico."},{"time":549000,"text":"So we brought her home,"},{"time":551000,"text":"and I prayed that the oil wouldn't wash up on her beach"},{"time":553000,"text":"before she died."},{"time":555000,"text":"And gratefully, it didn't."},{"time":557000,"text":"And she died quietly in her favorite place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560000,"text":"And a few weeks later, I was in New Orleans,"},{"time":562000,"text":"and this beautiful, spiritual friend"},{"time":564000,"text":"told me she wanted to do a healing for me."},{"time":566000,"text":"And I was honored."},{"time":568000,"text":"And I went to her house, and it was morning,"},{"time":570000,"text":"and the morning New Orleans sun was filtering through the curtains."},{"time":573000,"text":"And my friend was preparing this big bowl,"},{"time":575000,"text":"and I said, \"What is it?\""},{"time":577000,"text":"And she said, \"It's for you."},{"time":579000,"text":"The flowers make it beautiful,"},{"time":582000,"text":"and the honey makes it sweet.\""},{"time":584000,"text":"And I said, \"But what's the water part?\""},{"time":586000,"text":"And in the name of connectedness,"},{"time":588000,"text":"she said, \"Oh, it's the Gulf of Mexico.\""},{"time":591000,"text":"And I said, \"Of course it is.\""},{"time":593000,"text":"And the other women arrived and they sat in a circle,"},{"time":595000,"text":"and Michaela bathed my head with the sacred water."},{"time":598000,"text":"And she sang -- I mean her whole body sang."},{"time":601000,"text":"And the other women sang"},{"time":603000,"text":"and they prayed for me and my mother."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605000,"text":"And as the warm Gulf washed over my naked head,"},{"time":608000,"text":"I realized that it held"},{"time":610000,"text":"the best and the worst of us."},{"time":613000,"text":"It was the greed and recklessness"},{"time":615000,"text":"that led to the drilling explosion."},{"time":618000,"text":"It was all the lies that got told"},{"time":620000,"text":"before and after."},{"time":622000,"text":"It was the honey in the water that made it sweet,"},{"time":624000,"text":"it was the oil that made it sick."},{"time":627000,"text":"It was my head that was bald --"},{"time":629000,"text":"and comfortable now without a hat."},{"time":631000,"text":"It was my whole self"},{"time":633000,"text":"melting into Michaela's lap."},{"time":635000,"text":"It was the tears that were indistinguishable from the Gulf"},{"time":638000,"text":"that were falling down my cheek."},{"time":640000,"text":"It was finally being in my body."},{"time":645000,"text":"It was the sorrow"},{"time":647000,"text":"that's taken so long."},{"time":649000,"text":"It was finding my place"},{"time":651000,"text":"and the huge responsibility"},{"time":653000,"text":"that comes with connection."},{"time":655000,"text":"It was the continuing devastating war in the Congo"},{"time":658000,"text":"and the indifference of the world."},{"time":660000,"text":"It was the Congolese women"},{"time":662000,"text":"who are now rising up."},{"time":664000,"text":"It was my mother leaving,"},{"time":666000,"text":"just at the moment"},{"time":668000,"text":"that I was being born."},{"time":670000,"text":"It was the realization"},{"time":672000,"text":"that I had come very close to dying --"},{"time":674000,"text":"in the same way that the Earth, our mother,"},{"time":677000,"text":"is barely holding on,"},{"time":680000,"text":"in the same way that 75 percent of the planet"},{"time":684000,"text":"are hardly scraping by,"},{"time":687000,"text":"in the same way"},{"time":689000,"text":"that there is a recipe for survival."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692000,"text":"What I learned"},{"time":694000,"text":"is it has to do with attention and resources"},{"time":697000,"text":"that everybody deserves."},{"time":699000,"text":"It was advocating friends"},{"time":701000,"text":"and a doting sister."},{"time":703000,"text":"It was wise doctors and advanced medicine"},{"time":705000,"text":"and surgeons who knew what to do with their hands."},{"time":708000,"text":"It was underpaid and really loving nurses."},{"time":712000,"text":"It was magic healers and aromatic oils."},{"time":715000,"text":"It was people who came with spells and rituals."},{"time":717000,"text":"It was having a vision of the future"},{"time":720000,"text":"and something to fight for,"},{"time":722000,"text":"because I know this struggle isn't my own."},{"time":725000,"text":"It was a million prayers."},{"time":727000,"text":"It was a thousand hallelujahs"},{"time":729000,"text":"and a million oms."},{"time":731000,"text":"It was a lot of anger,"},{"time":733000,"text":"insane humor,"},{"time":735000,"text":"a lot of attention, outrage."},{"time":737000,"text":"It was energy, love and joy."},{"time":740000,"text":"It was all these things."},{"time":742000,"text":"It was all these things."},{"time":744000,"text":"It was all these things"},{"time":746000,"text":"in the water, in the world, in my body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":749000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}